    <description>Updates Latest Sequence and Latest Call Disposition on the Contact or Lead when a task is logged from Outreach
11/21/23 - Following Rev.io migration, updated Call Disposition values for &quot;Spoke to DM&quot; and &quot;Spoke to Non DM&quot;. (Revenue.io Implementation Project)
06-04-25 - BW - Updated to async to reduce record lock issues
10-30-25 - AC - Updating to remove references to Call Disposition</description>
